<h4>1.2.2 - 06 September 2022</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix - If delayed and date notifications were active, the date notifs would also get rescheduled. Fixed by changing the way the plugin detects notifications in order to delete them is the time is past</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.2.1 - 05 September 2022</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Various minor fixes applied</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.2.0 - 05 September 2022</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Feature - configured REST API to allow for remote cron jobs calls</li>
    <li>Feature - added option in Gravity Forms settings -> Notifications Delay to choose between remote and local cron job</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.1.1 - 11 August 2022</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix - for date delayed notifications, the main notification was not added</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.1.0 - 11 August 2022</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Feature - added notification delay at specific date</li>
    <li>Feature - it is now possible to define multiple future dates at which the same notification will be sent</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.0.0 - 27 July 2022</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Initial release</li>
</ul>
